{
  "texts": [
    "However, a need for development was defined due to different applications and evolutions in this field.",
    "One participant stated, \"Having digital resources and being able to use them is not sufficient to be digitally literate.",
    "We must be able to use, understand and produce information (P.7).",
    "\"The students welcomed new technological developments such as robotic surgery, decision support software, and prostheses.",
    "One participant said, \"If we talk about robotic surgery in the operating room, serious errors can even be reduced to zero."
  ]
}